' *** BLEND.LST ***                                  2nd GFA-Manual, page 20-23
> PROCEDURE blend(adr%,mode%,delay)
  '
  ' *** Fade-over from picture on address adr% (SPUT-string) to the screen
  ' *** Variable mode% (1-32000) determines effect; try 1, 7, 8, 9
  ' *** Variable delay& (ò 0) determines speed
  ' *** Procedure is less suitable for Medium or Low resolution
  ' *** Routine BLEND.INL (68 bytes) must be in INLINE-line blend%
  '
  ' *** Global:  blend% [INLINE-address]
  '
  VOID C:blend%(L:adr%,L:mode%,delay)
RETURN
' *********
'
